{"_path":"/record/disease/2022-06-14-disease","_dir":"disease","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","_empty":false,"title":"中暑","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"中暑"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中暑"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"迅速带入"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"是否跟连环梦有关系？不停的梦——醒——梦——醒……不知是醒是梦，apple watch记录只醒了3次在昨夜。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"八时一刻，起床，站不稳，头极其晕，扶墙去开了窗帘。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"马桶，回来，直接趴床上，汗出了，落，落了又出，盯着猫猫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"喝了半杯水，想要呕吐。汗，还是出了落，落了出。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"看了看温度，均温26.6，没理由中暑啊！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"出门下楼，感觉非常想吐，但还是在早餐店吃了包子。吃完感觉极其想吐。顺便吃了一粒感康。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"就回到家里，蹲在马桶前。没吐出来。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"喝了两支藿香正气水，不得不说，提神醒脑，似乎瞬间好了许多。但，仍然晕乎。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"此时，已九时两刻，打车公司，路上仍然犯晕，但呕吐之意尽无。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"似乎在藿香正气水的作用下结束了？"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.record:disease:2022-06-14-disease.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.record/disease/2022-06-14-disease.md","_extension":"md"}